          "target": "跳转至 {body}。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "The Midnight Line waits at the far platform. {traveler} has a ticket, a lantern, and a watch no one should recognize.",
          "target": "午夜列车停在远处的站台。{traveler}持有一张车票、一盏提灯，以及一块无人应识的怀表。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "A visual frame for the station-side beats. This one is not an Events Sheet row.",
          "target": "用于站台侧场景节拍的视觉框架。此框架并非事件表行。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "Custom Story Sequence frame. Event Frame is the behavior type; this is one concrete class built on it.",
          "target": "自定义故事序列框架。事件框架是行为类型；这是基于它构建的一个具体类。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "Fog swallows the rails. The watch once owned by @Old Reyes is heavier than it looks in {traveler}'s coat.",
          "target": "雾气吞没了铁轨。曾属于@Old Reyes的怀表，在{traveler}的外套里显得比看起来更沉。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "Tickets, please. {traveler}, is it? The Line has been waiting for that watch.",
          "target": "请出示车票。{traveler}，对吗？这趟列车一直在等待那块怀表。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "lantern_lit = true",
          "target": "lantern_lit = true"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "The variable table includes string, number, boolean, and json values. Open Playbook.json to inspect them.",
          "target": "变量表包含字符串、数字、布尔值和JSON值。请打开Playbook.json进行查看。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "Choice, Set, and branch outcome nodes inside the custom Story Sequence event-frame class.",
          "target": "自定义故事序列事件框架类内的选择、设置和分支结果节点。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "A gloved hand opens between you and the aisle.",
          "target": "一只戴着手套的手在你和过道之间伸出。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "trust_level = 2",
          "target": "trust_level = 2"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "{traveler} slips the watch deeper into her coat. The Brakeman notices the movement.",
          "target": "{traveler}将怀表更深地滑入外套。制动员注意到了这个动作。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "Radio check. If the lantern is lit, follow the blue carriage marks.",
          "target": "无线电检查。如果提灯亮着，就跟随蓝色车厢标记。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "Custom Event Frame. Its fields appear as extra Events Sheet columns for this group.",
          "target": "自定义事件框架。其字段会作为此组的额外事件表列显示。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "trust_level >= 2 && lantern_lit == true",
          "target": "trust_level >= 2 && lantern_lit == true"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "A brittle key catches lantern light. It is stamped with Reyes's maker mark.",
          "target": "一把易碎的钥匙在提灯光下闪烁。上面印有Reyes的制造商标记。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "The Conductor nods. A door unlocks that was never printed on the map.",
          "target": "列车长点了点头。一扇从未在地图上标注过的门解锁了。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "The Brakeman blocks the aisle. {traveler} has to bluff with a ticket and a dark lantern.",
          "target": "制动员挡住了过道。{traveler}不得不用车票和一盏熄灭的提灯虚张声势。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "Jump and epilogue beats gathered into the final Story Sequence frame.",
          "target": "跳转和尾声节拍汇集到最终的故事序列框架中。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
          "source": "Terminus",
          "target": "终点站"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "body",
